  <h3>Wednesday Afternoon Coworking</h3>
  <p>Each Wednesday at 1 p.m. at Mahtay Cafe</p>

  <p>
    Come work with fellow creatives, bounce ideas off one another, solve problems
    and share successes.
  </p>

